Changes in Version 1.2-3

  o hcl-colors.pdf removed from source ball (vignette now in colorspace)

Changes in Version 1.2-2

  o strucplot() now accepts a `df` argument that is passed to the shading
    functions. Also, expected values are no longer
    computed if residuals are given.

Changes in Version 1.2-1

  o Fixed a bug in labeling (incorrect handling of some parameters)

Changes in Version 1.2-0

  o Moved color palettes from vcd to colorspace,
    including vignette("hcl-colors"). Package colorspace
    is (as before) loaded automatically with vcd.

